---
import CornellNote from '../../../components/CornellNote.astro';

// LaTeX constants
const limConst = "$\\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 2}$";
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>유형 05. 0/0 꼴 (무리식) - 상세 연습</title>
		<!-- KaTeX -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			body {
				background-color: #e0e0e0;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<CornellNote title="유형 05. 0/0 꼴 (무리식)" chapter="Chapter 01 Practice">
			
			<div slot="cues">
				<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">💡 집중 공략 포인트</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>무리식이 보이면 먼저 **켤레식** 곱하기</li>
					<li>유리화를 통해 분모/분자에서 공통인수 추출</li>
					<li>약분 후 극한값 대입</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<section>
				<div class="type-section">
					<h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 2px solid #e63946; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
						[핵심 문제]
					</h4>
					<p>다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
					<div style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.6rem; margin: 40px 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.02); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px;">
						<span class="math">{limConst} { "$ \\frac{\\sqrt{x+2} - 2}{x - 2} $" }</span>
					</div>
					
					<!-- Progressive Disclosure: Strategy -->
					<details style="margin-top: 30px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; background: #fff;">
						<summary style="font-weight: bold; color: #1a73e8; cursor: pointer; padding: 5px;">💡 해결 전략 (클릭하여 확인)</summary>
						<div style="margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px; border-top: 1px dashed #eee; color: #444; line-height: 1.6;">
							무리식이 포함된 { "$ 0/0 $" } 꼴입니다. <b>유리화</b>를 통해 분자에서 { "$ (x-2) $" } 인수를 끄집어내는 것이 핵심입니다.
						</div>
					</details>

					<!-- Progressive Disclosure: Step-by-Step Solution -->
					<details style="margin-top: 15px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; background: #fff;">
						<summary style="font-weight: bold; color: #e63946; cursor: pointer; padding: 5px;">📝 단계별 풀이 (마지막에 열어보세요!)</summary>
						<div style="margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px; border-top: 1px dashed #eee; color: #444; line-height: 1.8;">
							<p><b>Step 1. 형태 확인 및 켤레식 설정</b><br/>$x \to 2$일 때 $0/0$ 꼴이므로 분자의 켤레식인 { "$ (\\sqrt{x+2} + 2) $" }를 분모와 분자에 각각 곱합니다.</p>
							<p><b>Step 2. 유리화 진행</b><br/>분자는 { "$ (x+2) - 4 = x-2 $" }가 됩니다.</p>
							<p><b>Step 3. 약분 후 마무리</b><br/>분모와 분자의 { "$ (x-2) $" }를 약분하면 분모에 { "$ (\\sqrt{x+2} + 2) $" }만 남습니다.<br/>
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 2} \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{x+2} + 2} = \\frac{1}{2+2} = \\frac{1}{4} $" } 입니다.</p>
						</div>
					</details>

					<!-- Difficulty Level Navigation -->
					<div style="margin-top: 50px; padding: 25px; background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #eee;">
						<p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #333; font-size: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
							🎯 내 실력에 맞는 문제 도전하기
						</p>
						<div style="display: flex; gap: 12px;">
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/levels/type05-low/" style="flex: 1; padding: 15px; background: #eef7ee; color: #2e7d32; text-align: center; border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border: 1.5px solid #2e7d32; font-size: 1.3rem;">
								[하]
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<a href="/wiki/chapter01/problems-const/" class="back-link" style="margin-top: 40px; display: inline-block;">← 유형별 목록으로 돌아가기</a>
			</section>

			<div slot="summary">
				<p>루트($\sqrt{\quad}$)가 있더라도 당황하지 마세요. **'유리화'**만 하면 결국 다항식 문제와 똑같은 원점(약분)으로 돌아옵니다!</p>
			</div>
		</CornellNote>

		<script is:inline>
			if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
				document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
					if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
						renderMathInElement(document.body, {
							delimiters: [
								{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
								{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
							],
							throwOnError : false
						});
					}
				});
			}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
